description:
It's valentines day and the Sonic Underground characters are all struggling to figure out what to get each other on this heartpounding day. Well... everybody except for Bartleby and Sonic of course, because they already know just how much they love each other lol

Starring all your favorite characters,
Bartleby Montclair of Dresdin
Sonic the Hedgehog
Manic the Hedgehog
Sonia the Hedgehog
Knuckles the Echidna
Mindy Latour
Uncle Chuck
Queen Aleena
